{"type": "article", "id": 13341, "title": "如果你要在树林里盖房子，你也会盖这种37米长的吗？", "description": "灰色的外立面，温馨的内部空间，建筑师说这种形状是对自然环境的回应\r\n", "date": "2015-08-11T18:12:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14332, "name": "奥地利"}, {"id": 11871, "name": "住宅"}, {"id": 14333, "name": "长房子"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021209175wRKbVUX2TopMFqW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>37 </span>米长的住宅长啥样？奥地利的福拉尔贝格州树林外面，出现了一幢长 <span>37 </span>米的住宅，建筑师认为细长的构造是对自然条件简单的回应。房子的外立面是深灰色，内部则多使用木材料，塑造温馨的空间。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120911eYsrIAw1izyx5hOC.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"建筑有着灰色的外立面\" alt=\"建筑有着灰色的外立面\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>灰色的外立面，<span>窗户开口挺有韵律感</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120911rDEtYIZ105BTMvjh.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"窗户\" alt=\"窗户\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>窗户</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120911DFZiXJH6VMA7E1mR.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"472\" title=\"建筑物入口处\" alt=\"建筑物入口处\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>建筑物入口处</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这个房子的业主是一家年轻人，他们不仅在房子内居住，还在其中办公，每一层都拥有各自的入口。<span style=\"text-align:center;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120912SxnsqPypVbmg2i0M.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"工作区域\" alt=\"工作区域\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>工作区域</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120912nw0MWUYfebyEu6ph.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"内部构造\" alt=\"内部构造\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>内部构造</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120913ofFEqZkX26peQ8Rn.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"内部构造\" alt=\"内部构造\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>内部构造</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120914CzlXjQZTd7Rfeyvi.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"卧室\" alt=\"卧室\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">阅读室\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021209142aOHqV4fBRbLDCMz.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"472\" title=\"阅读室\" alt=\"阅读室\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>阅读室</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120915ipXyCvLqRP9FbS4t.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"472\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">餐厅及活动空间\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120915EguGqa73dRXb0vIP.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"建筑物夜晚的样子\" alt=\"建筑物夜晚的样子\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>建筑物夜晚的样子</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这幢房子是由建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://www.juritroy.at/\">juri troy\r\narchitects</a> 设计完成的，他们还有一些其他项目：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120916UloASBQgamMR1we7.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" title=\"木屋\" alt=\"木屋\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>木屋</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120916Zk48MzUVDfdBlGch.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" title=\"另外一个木屋\" alt=\"另外一个木屋\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>另外一个木屋</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.gooood.hk/37m-in-hohenems-juri-troy.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><em>gooood</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}